 of Indonesia]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{wikivoyage|Derawan}}\n\n{{coord|2|15|N|118|25|E|source:kolossus-frwiki|display=title}}\n{{Tourist attractions in Indonesia}}\n\n{{East Kalimantan}}\n\n[[Category:Derawan Islands| ]]\n[[Category:Archipelagoes of Indonesia]]\n[[Category:Landforms of East Kalimantan]]\n[[Category:Islands of Kalimantan]]\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Derawan_Islands"}
