}\n{{Div col end}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Willy Brandt}}\n{{Wikiquote}}\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20150505062201/http://www.willy-brandt.de/en/foundation.html The Federal Chancellor Willy Brandt Foundation]\n*[http://www.willy-brandt-forum.com Willy-Brandt-Forum in Unkel]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20120322233043/http://www.bwbs.de/bwbs_biografie/index_en.html Official Biography of Willy Brandt] by Chancellor Willy Brandt Foundation\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20060721023939/http://www.globalautonomy.ca/global1/glossary_entry.jsp?id=EV.0025 Adam Sneyd, \"Brandt Commission\"] in Globalization and Autonomy Online Compendium, edited by William D. Coleman and Nancy Johnson\n*[http://www.brandt21forum.info/Bio_Brandt.htm Biography of Willy Brandt]\n*[http://www.cvce.eu/recherche/unit-content/-/unit/f28057ae-f00f-4677-8327-d97d19023b80 Willy Brandt and the unification of Europe] from Center for European Studies collection\n*[http://www.depauw.edu/news/index.asp?id=17907 Ubben Lecture] at DePauw University\n*{{C-SPAN|Willy Brandt}}\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-off}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Otto Suhr]]|rows=2}}\n{{s-ttl|title=President of the [[Abgeordnetenhaus of Berlin|West Berlin House of Representatives]]|years=1955\u20131957}}\n{{s-aft|after={{ill|Kurt Landsberg|de}}}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Governing Mayor of Berlin|Mayor of West Berlin]]|years=1957\u20131966}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Heinrich Albertz]]}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Kurt Sieveking]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[President of the German Bundesrat|President of the Bundesrat]]|years=1957\u20131958}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Wilhelm Kaisen]]}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Gerhard Schr\u00f6der (CDU)|Gerhard Schr\u00f6der]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Minister for Foreign Affairs (Germany)|Federal Minister for Foreign Affairs]]|years=1966\u20131969}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Walter Scheel]]|rows=2}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Hans-Christoph Seebohm]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Vice Chancellor of Germany|Vice Chancellor of West Germany]]|years=1966\u20131969}}\n{{