{"title_page": "2010\u201311 Club Am\u00e9rica season", "text_new": "{{Infobox football club season\n| club             = [[Club Am\u00e9rica|Am\u00e9rica]]\n| season           = 2010\u201311\n| chairman         = \n| manager          = \n| stadium          = [[Estadio Azteca]]\n| league           = [[2010\u201311 Primera Divisi\u00f3n de M\u00e9xico season#Torneo Apertura|Apertura 2011]]\n| league result    = 4th\n| league2          = [[2010\u201311 Primera Divisi\u00f3n de M\u00e9xico season#Torneo Clausura|Clausura 2012]]\n| league2 result   = 6th\n| cup2             =\n| cup2 result      =\n| cup1             =\n| cup1 result      =\n| cup3             =\n| cup3 result      =\n| league topscorer = <br>Apertura: [[Vicente Mat\u00edas Vuoso]] (8) Clausura: [[\u00c1ngel Reyna]] (13) \n| season topscorer = Vicente Mat\u00edas Vuoso (15)\n| prevseason       = [[2009\u201310 Club Am\u00e9rica season|2009\u201310]]\n| nextseason       = [[2011\u201312 Club Am\u00e9rica season|2011\u201312]]\n| pattern_la1      = |pattern_b1=_america1112h|pattern_ra1=\n| leftarm1         = 000060|body1=FFFF00|rightarm1=000060|shorts1=FFFF00|socks1=FFFF00\n| pattern_la2      = |pattern_b2=_america1112a|pattern_ra2=\n| leftarm2         = 000060|body2=000060|rightarm2=000060|shorts2=000060|socks2=000060\n| t                = s\n}}\n\nThe 2010&ndash;11 '''[[Club Am\u00e9rica|Am\u00e9rica]]''' season was the 64th professional season of Mexico's top-flight football league. The season is split into two tournaments&mdash;the Torneo Apertura and the Torneo Clausura&mdash;each with identical formats and each contested by the same eighteen teams. Am\u00e9rica will begin their season on July 24, 2010 against [[C.F. Pachuca|Pachuca]].\n\n==Torneo Apertura==\n\n===Squad===\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player | no= 1 | nat=MEX | pos=GK | name= [[Guillermo Ochoa]]|other=[[Captain (association football)|Captain]]}}\n{{Fs player | no= 2 | nat=MEX | pos=DF | name= [[Ismael de Jes\u00fas Rodr\u00edguez|Ismael Rodr\