zo]], [[Zapopan, Jalisco|Zapopan]]\n|attendance=\n|referee=Francisco Chac\u00f3n\n|result=w\n|stack=yes\n}}\n\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|round= Round 16\n|team1=[[Club Am\u00e9rica|Am\u00e9rica]] \n|date=April 24, 2011\n|time=4:00pm\n|score= 1 &ndash; 1\n|report=[http://www.mediotiempo.com/ficha.php?id_partido=33452 Report]\n|team2=[[Atlante F.C.|Atlante]] \n|goals1= [[\u00c1ngel Reyna|Reyna]] {{goal|35}}\n|goals2= [[Giancarlo Maldonado|Maldonado]] {{goal|38}}\n|stadium=\n|location=[[Estadio Azteca]], [[Mexico City]]\n|attendance=\n|referee=Mauricio Morales \n|result=d\n|stack=yes\n}}\n\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|round= Round 17\n|team1=[[Club Universidad Nacional|UNAM]] \n|date=May 1, 2011\n|time=12:00pm\n|score=0 &ndash; 2\n|report=[http://www.mediotiempo.com/ficha.php?id_partido=33528 Report]\n|team2=[[Club Am\u00e9rica|Am\u00e9rica]] \n|goals1= \n|goals2= [[Vicente Mat\u00edas Vuoso|Vuoso]] {{goal|59}}<br>[[\u00c1ngel Reyna|Reyna]] {{goal|90+1}}\n|stadium=\n|location=[[Estadio Ol\u00edmpico Universitario]], [[Mexico City]]\n|attendance=\n|referee=Ricardo Arellano \n|result=w\n|stack=\n}}\n\n====Final phase====\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|round= Quarterfinals\n|team1=[[Club Am\u00e9rica|Am\u00e9rica]] \n|date=May 5, 2011\n|time=9:00pm\n|score=1 &ndash; 2\n|report=[http://www.mediotiempo.com/ficha.php?id_partido=35147 Report]\n|team2=[[Monarcas Morelia|Morelia]]\n|goals1= [[Daniel M\u00e1rquez|M\u00e1rquez]] {{goal|70}}\n|goals2=[[Manuel P\u00e9rez Flores|M.&nbsp;P\u00e9rez]] {{goal|16}}<br>[[Rafael M\u00e1rquez Lugo|M\u00e1rquez]] {{goal|61}}\n|stadium=\n|location=[[Estadio Corregidora]], [[Quer\u00e9taro, Quer\u00e9taro|Quer\u00e9taro]]<ref>Due to a [[U2 360\u00b0 Tour|U2]] concert at [[Estadio Azteca]], Am\u00e9rica had to play their home game in Quer\u00e9taro</ref>\n|attendance=\n|referee=Paul Delgadillo\n|result=l\n|stack=yes\n}}\n\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|round= Quarterfinals\n|team1=[[Monarcas Morelia|Morelia]]\n|date=May 8, 2011\n|time=8:00pm\n|s